msg":"你幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知唔知咩叫洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bda44f6cf535cfdfddc97bbd8aa7559a5265af8","tid":1044210,"uid":96877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"一個月萬五至二萬五叫搵快錢？<br />\n樓主做緊份咩工？"},{"pid":"881d3ba5d70a80387393f023bd22a347454129c8","tid":1044210,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"259f49fea738db90bf0f62124f207ca5ae777b9e","tid":1044210,"uid":168787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88689cb7a55456580528224ecbc936e725996aaa","tid":1044210,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d291c11610ff39c6c5885098e1105cdc6893a5e9","tid":1044210,"uid":168787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"可以點呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:53:49.000Z","msg":"搵過佢話係公司做假數借銀行戶口出糧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你自己寫左啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"犯咩法 純粹想問下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:05:56.000Z","msg":"無論任何情況，銀行戶口都唔能夠借畀其他人用。你去銀行開戶口時，銀行核對過你嘅身份證明，了解過你嘅戶口用途，先至開戶口畀你。戶口借咗畀人用，就同你之前向銀行申報嘅用途有出入，萬一涉及不法活動，分分鐘會變成「洗黑錢」。 <br />\n<br />\n所謂「洗黑錢」，就係不法份子將喺販毒、貪污、避稅、詐騙等等呢啲非法活動收取嘅「黑錢」，透過各種手段，例如借用良民嘅戶口，以掩飾呢啲錢嘅來源。「處理犯罪得益」罪，即係洗黑錢，最高刑罪係罰款500萬港元同埋監禁14年。<br />\n<br />\n如果你戶口借出去涉及不法活動，就好大機會當你有份參與㗎嘞。新聞都經常有呢類報道，有啲人出於好心抑或貪心而借出戶口被人洗錢，上到法庭個陣用「唔知情」求情，最後都會被判罪。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/key-information/column/20180601.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fkey-information%2Fcolumn%2F20180601.shtml&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=65085252\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/key-information/column/20180601.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"e1254e250dd7ec357ebe0aeb11bd969c6fceb253","tid":1044210,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:10:59.000Z","msg":"你弱智?"},{"pid":"2dda00331dd72a0e2511c17eb72f095e95c8e6fb","tid":1044210,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:41:31.000Z","msg":"絕對合法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n此地無銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413ce8908ff4aa58c257ed21714538e428eb7ee1","tid":1044210,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:43:12.000Z","msg":"仲九成？"},{"pid":"2d58891291bad50d336d480d17d47670472fc9a0","tid":1044210,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"259f49fea738db90bf0f62124f207ca5ae777b9e","tid":1044210,"uid":168787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88689cb7a55456580528224ecbc936e725996aaa","tid":1044210,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d291c11610ff39c6c5885098e1105cdc6893a5e9","tid":1044210,"uid":168787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"可以點呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:53:49.000Z","msg":"搵過佢話係公司做假數借銀行戶口出糧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你自己寫左啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"犯咩法 純粹想問下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:43:44.000Z","msg":"弱智唔好上網，乖乖地做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ce5ca831cdc62db437149a2e9dc5501211ad5e","tid":1044210,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:44:31.000Z","msg":"佢話絕對合法喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該唔係呃人"},{"pid":"8508a0fdbf2ba03b0cd8a494b64e9e0d1b5c03a2","tid":1044210,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:52:13.000Z","msg":"IG變咗騙徒集中地"},{"pid":"c287220260863514f151fb06b3ec402de87a38a7","tid":1044210,"uid":129704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18: